{"tid":31853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸仔洗澡不慎滑倒　遭水龍頭深插入背","createTime":"2016-12-10T01:39:46.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-10T05:17:41.000Z","uid":122,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dde91429b91d9b9b971cb477ce29796c4aca611d","tid":31853,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T01:39:46.000Z","msg":"12月 9日(五) 23:28<br />\n<strong>驚！粵漢洗澡不慎滑倒　遭水龍頭深插入背</strong><br />\n<br />\n廣東珠海市昨日發生一宗罕見的家居意外，一名李姓男子下午洗澡時不慎滑倒，期間背部貼着牆壁滑下，由於衝力甚大，安裝在牆壁下方的水龍頭開關柄直插入李的背部後並斷開，開關柄深入李的背部5厘米，鮮血直流。<br />\n<br />\n事後，李男被送往醫院救治，經醫院心胸外科醫生進行手術，將水龍頭開關柄取出，目前李男正在康復之中。內地媒體指，今次發生在李男身上的家居意外，此前也曾經發生過；另有裝修業內人士表示，沖涼房內的水龍頭安裝不當，或將變成傷人利器。"},{"pid":"f0ecee2499dd5d937fa8be1be13d426421afe50e","tid":31853,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T01:41:21.000Z","msg":"竟然未死"},{"pid":"8bd67cb98138f4c9490bcea45f7c289b1a22ac02","tid":31853,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T01:42:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3149491f0edcea8c8959ad520287cea6a030b4de","tid":31853,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T02:03:10.000Z","msg":"係背脊開水喉放血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a1241995b056de255dca93ebc2c7eb1cbb1052c","tid":31853,"uid":13505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T02:05:44.000Z","msg":"發生過類似 但冇插入去 浴缸冇扶手真係幾危險吓"},{"pid":"4eae374d881b3a24a0e143939cd4dce77616fe8c","tid":31853,"uid":22422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T02:14:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99704afbfd639ab149e73bae6e29c5f167f245ab","tid":31853,"uid":51649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T02:17:21.000Z","msg":"腳仔